snippet.title: Parkour Legends Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Parkour Legends is a 2D precision platformer that gives players the adrenaline rush of free running with extensive mechanics, tight controls, and blissful movement that's chill, yet challenging.

Coming 2023 -- WISHLIST NOW on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2115130/Parkour_Legends/?utm_source=youtube_announcement

Join the official Discord for access to the private Alpha Demo
https://discord.gg/PUWF84gwaU
